ckquote>全靠中岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d0a84b9ddfb72db844623362d232d2c3cd832d","tid":491284,"uid":137719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全靠中岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n耶撚永遠話自己婚前唔扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n耶撚結婚應該驗下係咪處先"},{"pid":"fc9bbe0c115bc24a6a228c2575e98b176f887a79","tid":491284,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:35:37.000Z","msg":"條女正撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e1c21f2a54b1bbf34d96874737faf8942e95b0","tid":491284,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"舊愛梁嘉琪<br />\n<br />\n[[檔案:]] 當張繼聰和謝安琪傳出未婚懷孕籌備婚禮的時候，有報刊記者翻舊帳提及他和演藝同學梁嘉琪的一段情。當時更傳聞謝安琪為第三者，「大肚逼婚」硬拆散鴛鴦等等。[3]張繼聰在2007年澄清他的確是和梁嘉琪拍過五年拖，但亦已分手五年，中間更曾有幾任女友，所以Kay（謝安琪英文名）與嘉琪根本沒有關係。[4]<br />\n<br />\n不過傳聞並未因此平息，更隨著謝安琪走紅，以及梁嘉琪正式在《學警狙擊》一劇作幕前演出而越演越烈。相關「舊聞」不斷被記者重提，網民對此亦不時作出討論。[5][6]有網民更在梁嘉琪的網誌留言暗示她因保守，因不肯婚前讓張生搞大自己個肚而令他成了別人的丈夫。[7]<br />\n<br />\n2010年1月張繼聰和梁嘉琪公開碰頭合照，梁嘉琪表示曾向Kay提及狗仔隊經常問及有關她夫妻二人的問題，Kay夫婦知道後也因累及她而覺得不好意思。[8]"},{"pid":"3d5ad4dff1ba03e7527be685d81784215ce4e05a","tid":491284,"uid":50253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"要好似張生咁識投資潛力股"},{"pid":"3b93307610f384f0619f517d3cdfc7b8112e4cae","tid":491284,"uid":46049,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T02